metadata.description: The Xylocats Ancestral NFT collection features 1,337 unique images of the Xylocat ancestors. The Xylocats are an ancient race of space-dwelling mystical beings. We know about them today based on signals received from The Archeologist. The information is still being decoded but what is known is that the basis of their advanced capabilities is a combination of technology and magic. For more information on the Xylocats visit the Xylocat Archives at www.xylocats.com to read about their homeworld.
